📦 Installation Guide for recon.py v5.0
bash:
# 1. Install dependencies
pip install dnspython python-whois

# 2. Download the script
# Option A: Using wget
wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lividbigpp/Livrecon/main/re

# Option B: Using curl
curl -O https://raw.githubusercontent.com/yourusername/recon-tool/main/reconv6.py
OR
# Option C: Just copy the raw file from GitHub

# 3. Run it
python3 reconv6.py example.com
